's success and hopes the investment will pay off in long term economic and social stability in beijing and throughout the country china views the 2008 olympics as both a celebration of cultural achievement and a critical opportunity to present its modernity to the world and to win global recognition as a thriving unified and powerful country interactive website beijing interactive game jeopardy parent publications cover nbc documentary the road to beijing nbc 2008 pdf+ cover yo yo ma and the silk road ensemble documentary the road to beijing 2008 pdf+ stanford university all rights reserved 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints rss+ rss xml feeds
